Coastal Waters Forecast
National Weather Service Baltimore MD/Washington DC
1034 AM EDT Fri Apr 8 2022

Tidal Potomac River and Maryland portion of Chesapeake Bay.

Forecasts of wave heights do not include effects of wind direction
relative to tidal currents. Expect higher waves when winds are
blowing against the tidal flow.  

ANZ500-082000-
1034 AM EDT Fri Apr 8 2022

.SYNOPSIS FOR THE TIDAL POTOMAC AND MD PORTION OF THE CHESAPEAKE BAY...

A trough will build overhead through the weekend. High pressure is 
expected to return for the start of the next work week. Small Craft 
Advisories may be needed for portions of the waters into the
weekend. 

